### Get all pods from all namespaces
GET http://localhost:4000/api/pods
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get all pods from specific namespace (using query parameter)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/pods?namespace=customer-cmdg67pz
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get all pods from specific namespace (using path parameter)
GET http://localhost:4000/api/namespaces/kube-system/pods
Content-Type: application/json

###

